Is it going to shoot again?
That is not good...

rows.label: bf09040100_0040
rows.name:
The Superbian Divine Beast is said 
to be at the end of its lifespan.

rows.label: bf09040100_0050
rows.name:
If it were to release any more of the ether energy
stored within its body...

rows.label: bf09040100_0070
rows.name:
It would collapse, its joints giving way
under its own weight...
